CCR#5: DRY

Suppose you have a code block that performs the same calculation multiple times:

result1 <- 2 * 3 + 4
result2 <- 2 * 5 + 4
result3 <- 2 * 7 + 4

Create a function to encapsulate this calculation and reuse it multiple times:

calculate <- function(x) {
  2 * x + 4
}

result1 <- calculate(3)
result2 <- calculate(5)
result3 <- calculate(7)





